target=3D_blank>The Keyed-Hash Message Authentication Code (HMAC) =
Validation=20
System (HMACVS)</A>. <STRONG>Additional testing note: </STRONG>All =
underlying=20
SHA algorithm(s) supported by the HMAC implementation must be validated =
as part=20
of the HMAC validation.</P>
<H3>Validation List:</H3>
