href=3D"http://csrc.nist.gov/groups/STM/cavp/documents/mac/hmacval.html" =

target=3D_blank>HMAC Validation List</A>.</P>
<H3>Test Vectors:</H3>
<P>HMAC Test Vectors - These files provide an electronic version of the =
test=20
vectors that can be used to informally verify the correctness of an HMAC =

algorithm implementation using the HMACVS. <EM><STRONG>However, use of =
these=20
vectors does not take the place of validation obtained through the =
Cryptographic=20
Algorithm Validation Program (CAVP).</STRONG></EM></P>
