<H2>Algorithm Component Validation Testing </H2>
<P>Beginning in 2011, the CAVP offers the validation of algorithm =
components.=20
There exists an increased need for the testing of individual components =
of=20
approved algorithms. Some examples of situations where algorithm =
component=20
testing will be required includes PIV Smartcard applications, where =
there are=20
processing limitations, and situations where parts of special =
publications can=20
be used with components outside the special publication. The components =
for=20
which we have validation testing are listed below.</P>
<H3>SP 800-56A Elliptic Curve Cryptography Cofactor Diffie-Hellman (ECC =
CDH)=20
Primitive Testing</H3>
<P>The testing of only the SP800-56A Section 5.7.1.2 <EM>Elliptic Curve=20
Cryptography Cofactor Diffie-Hellman (ECC CDH) Primitive</EM>.</P>
<UL class=3Dbullets1>
  <LI><A class=3Dpdf=20
  =
href=3D"http://csrc.nist.gov/publications/nistpubs/800-56A/SP800-56A_Revi=
sion1_Mar08-2007.pdf"=20
  target=3D_blank>NIST SP 800-56A </A>, <EM>Recommendation for Pair-Wise =
Key=20
  Establishment Schemes Using Discrete Logarithm Cryptography (Revised =
March=20
  2007), Section 5.7.1.2</EM>.</LI></UL>
<H3>Testing Requirements:</H3>
<P>Validation testing for SP800-56A Section 5.7.1.2 ECC CDH Primitive =
component=20
testing is handled by the Cryptographic Algorithm Validation Program's =
(<A=20
href=3D"http://csrc.nist.gov/groups/STM/cavp/index.html">CAVP</A>) <A=20
href=3D"http://csrc.nist.gov/groups/STM/testing_labs/index.html">CST =
labs</A>.=20
</P>
<UL class=3Dbullets1>
  <LI>ECC CDH Primitive tests are described in <A class=3Dpdf=20
  =
href=3D"http://csrc.nist.gov/groups/STM/cavp/documents/components/ecccdhv=
s.pdf"=20
  target=3D_blank>The Elliptic Curve Cryptography Cofactor =
Diffie_Hellman (ECC=20
  CDH) Primitive Validation System (ECC_CDHVS)</A>. </LI></UL>
<H3>Validation List:</H3>
<P>NIST maintains the current <A=20
href=3D"http://csrc.nist.gov/groups/STM/cavp/documents/components/compone=
ntval.html"=20
target=3D_blank>Component Validation List</A>. This CVL contains the =
validated=20
implementations of the ECC CDH Primitive. </P>
<H3>Other Information:</H3>
<UL class=3Dbullets1>
